headline: GHOST®, Cinnamon Toast Crunch™ and Lucky Charms™ Team Up to Deliver Protein-Packed Cereals
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, February 05, 2026--Get ready to level up your breakfast game! General Mills, in continued collaboration with lifestyle and sports nutrition brand GHOST®, is thrilled to announce the launch of two new crave-worthy, high-protein cereals: GHOST® PROTEIN CEREAL x CINNAMON TOAST CRUNCH™ and GHOST® PROTEIN CEREAL x LUCKY CHARMS™. headline: Heard on the Street Wednesday Recap: Tech Tantrum
summary: Tech stocks continued their selloff. Tuesday’s software rout spread Wednesday to AI-enabling stocks that had rallied a lot this year. The biggest loser in the Nasdaq-100 was chip maker Advanced Micro Devices, which fell 17% after reporting worse-than-expected results.
